{"word":"μυκτηρίζω","slug":"μυκτηρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μυκτηρίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:μυκτήρ'><el>μυκτήρ</el></a>\n<el>(μυκτηρίζω,) </el><p/><i>to turn up the nose</i> or <i>sneer at</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be mocked</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}